          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既是司徒王允之女，可知历代褒贬之事，"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小女子不知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道三杰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪三杰?"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周三杰、汉三杰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何为“周三杰”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周公、太公、召公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“汉三杰”呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张良、韩信、萧何。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自周朝以来，古今出了多少名将？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小女子才疏学浅，倘有差错，望二将军指教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且讲来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二将军容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前三皇后五帝道德为上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有尧舜和禹汤四大明王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "渭水河访贤臣定国安邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十二国钟无盐女中豪强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后七国有乐毅兵伐齐邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "光武帝整乾坤迁都洛阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一朝君一朝臣犬吠尧王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周文王梦飞熊夜入虎帐"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十八国伍子胥盟辅上将"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前七国有孙庞二人斗智"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前汉朝至平帝出了王莽"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小女子说不尽古今良将"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有关某闻言心中高兴，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个貂婵女与众不同。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "单问你虎牢关谁是英雄？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不问前朝的兴和废"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我闻言吃一惊心中暗想，"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "口问心心问口自己思量："
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但是难比刘、关、张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊一声二将军细听端详:"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "战沙场论英雄可算吕布"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走向前屈膝跪"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "论英雄三将军天下无双"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你丈夫吕布呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那吕布三姓奴臭名远扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可曾见过我那三弟？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虎牢关摆战场，"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金鼓声喧鬼神忙！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我那三弟他头戴？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "头戴着乌金盔盔缨灿亮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他身穿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身穿着乌油甲甲放毫光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胯下？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胯下一骑乌骓马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手使何物？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手使一杆丈八枪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一似黑煞神下了天堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在阵前吼一声犹如雷响"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在阵前吼一声犹如雷响"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个貂蝉女能言善讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言来语去有文章。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青锋剑斩她一命亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽拔剑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "貂蝉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可识此剑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小女子不知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此剑乃周文王所造，传到关某手中，遇有不平之事，它便做响！"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知响过几次了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "响过三次。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第一次？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斩颜良、诛文丑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "第二次？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "白门楼斩吕布。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这第三次呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这第三次么！帐前无人，恐怕要应在你的身上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二将军哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来心惊战，"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊一声二将军听我言："
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要斩我弱女子所为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你往日斩的是英雄汉"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我爱你怀揣忠义胆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "匡扶社稷你计献连环。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人虽亡美名儿留在世间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "功高盖世人称赞"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "风儿吹得烛光闪，"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云敛晴空月正圆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "貂蝉",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死得其所我心也甘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（貂蝉引头就刃。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关云长月下斩貂蝉！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽斩貂蝉死。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "弟兄结拜在桃园，三战吕布虎牢关。杀死颜良诛文丑，明月之下斩貂蝉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽、貂蝉同下。）"
        }
      ],
